00:22:25,818 --> 00:22:29,720
foremost thing, how to surrender to Reality.

216
00:22:30,540 --> 00:22:36,420
So, if you learn how to surrender to the Primordial Kundalini,

217
00:22:36,860 --> 00:22:39,993
then your Kundalini's immediately strengthened.

218
00:22:40,420 --> 00:22:45,140
It's like this, supposing you have a stone

219
00:22:45,340 --> 00:22:53,340
