222
00:23:02,500 --> 00:23:06,700
Then you have the glass. The glass won't reflect.

223
00:23:06,900 --> 00:23:11,140
But if you use some mercury and make it a mirror, it will reflect,

224
00:23:11,340 --> 00:23:14,060
but still it may not be the perfect mirror.

225
00:23:14,260 --> 00:23:18,660
So this is how the kind of a reflector you are,

226
00:23:18,860 --> 00:23:23,100
on that depends the kind of a reflection you get

227
00:23:23,300 --> 00:23:26,980
and the kind of personality you develop.

